# Implementation Plan - Affiliate Manual Refs & Analytics

This plan outlines the steps to implement a feature allowing users to manually track affiliate performance, separate official projects from AI-saved leads, and link ads campaigns for ROI analytics.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Data Persistence**: We are currently using `localStorage`. For large daily stats, this might reach limits eventually, but for a mock-up/MVP, it's sufficient.
> **Project Separation**: I will split the "Quản lý dự án" page into two main tabs: "Dự án chính thức" and "Dự án từ AI Agents".

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Data Model & Hook Updates
#### [MODIFY] [useProjects.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/hooks/useProjects.js)
- Update state to include `isOfficial` flag and `dailyStats` array.
- Add `promoteToOfficial(index)` function.
- Ensure `saveProject` handles new fields: `affiliateRef`, `linkedCampaignIds`.

### 2. Frontend: Navigation & Projects Page
#### [MODIFY] [ProjectsPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/ProjectsPage.jsx)
- Implement a Tab-based view at the top:
  - **Dự án chính thức**: Active projects with full analytics.
  - **Dự án từ AI Agents**: Leads saved from research/chat (Unofficial).
- Add "Thiết lập thành chính thức" button for unofficial projects.

### 3. Frontend: Project Details & Analytics
#### [MODIFY] [ProjectDetailPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/pages/ProjectDetailPage.jsx)
- Add a new tab: **Phân tích ROAS & CVR**.
- **Campaign Linking**: Interface to select which Ads Campaigns (from AdsContext) belong to this project.
- **Manual Daily Entry**: A simplified Excel-like grid to quickly input:
  - `RefCount` (Clicks/Leads from Affiliate Dashboard)
  - `Conversions` (Validated sales)
  - `Revenue` (Commission earned)
- **Analytics Visuals**:
  - ROAS Chart (Revenue vs Ads Spend).
  - CVR Chart (Conversions / RefCount).
  - Metric cards for Total Spend, Total Revenue, Net Profit, ROAS.

### 4. Component: Quick Daily Entry
#### [NEW] [DailyStatsModal.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/adecosmvp/frontend/src/components/DailyStatsModal.jsx)
- A dedicated modal to solve the "repetitive pain point" of manual entry.
- Features: Autocomplete for recent dates, easy tab-through fields, and "copy from yesterday" option.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- No automated tests currently in project, but I will verify components via manual inspection using the browser tool.

### Manual Verification
1. **Save a project from search results**: Verify it appears in the "Dự án từ AI Agents" tab.
2. **Promote to Official**: Verify it moves to the "Dự án chính thức" tab and gains the "Analytics" tab in details.
3. **Link Campaigns**: Link a mock campaign and verify "Spend" data is pulled into the project's analytics.
4. **Enter Daily Stats**: Insert manual data for 3 days and check if ROAS/CVR charts update correctly.
